    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have started to develop Religion beyond other skills, delving deeper into its possibilities.</p><p><strong>Core Feats</strong></p><ul><li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.x7EMZNMavris2aHY]{Student of the Canon}</li></ul><p>Choose one Skill Path and gain that path's Trained feat.</p><p><strong>Available Skill Paths</strong></p><ul><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.7spp7DgHflR9LSjK]{Spellcraft (Religion) Path - Trained}</strong>: Your excellent knowledge of spells helps you identifying spells with great success.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.nkr3UfXsotNjLun2]{Itemcraft (Religion) Path - Trained}</strong>: Your knowledge of magical items empowers you use them to beyond their limits.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.lbOJefoI1Wz6pq19]{Faith Path - Trained}</strong>: You are a well-informed member of your faith.</li></ul>",
